data.title: Best Massage I Have Ever Had!
data.text: On a recent trip to Missouri, my friend and I wanted to get a massage. We happened upon The Oasis by searching online. It was very easy to find and the ladies were very nice. I will say this was the best massage I have ever had in my life. I get massages monthly and I sure wish I could have brought this place back home with me. After the massage I felt like a brand new person. I would highly recommend this place as it was affordable and the perfect relaxing afternoon. All I can say is WOW...this place is #1 in my books.
